{
  "name": "腐化信标",
  "category": "anvilcraft:smithing_system",
  "icon": "anvilcraft:corrupted_beacon",
  "sortnum": 13004,
  "entry_color": "004400",
  "extra_recipe_mappings": {
    "anvilcraft:corrupted_beacon": 1
  },
  "pages": [
    {
      "type": "patchouli:text",
      "text": "释放了被封印在信标之中的凋灵之力。会赋予光柱内的生物$(thing)凋零$()效果，部分生物会转化为另一种生物，还可以配合铁砧加工。"
    },
    {
      "type": "patchouli:spotlight",
      "anchor": "corrupted_beacon",
      "item": "anvilcraft:corrupted_beacon",
      "text": "完全使用$(l:smithing/tier_1_materials#cursed_gold_block)诅咒金块$()作为信标底座，并使用$(l:smithing/tier_1_materials#cursed_gold_ingot)诅咒金锭$()激活信标，则信标有概率转化为$(item)腐化信标$()。底座层数越多，转化概率越大。使用诅咒金锭激活信标时天气将转为雷雨天。"
    },
    "生物转化：$(br)$(thing)猪$()→$(thing)疣猪兽$()$(br)$(thing)牛$()→$(thing)劫掠兽$()$(br)$(thing)守卫者$()→$(thing)远古守卫者$()$(br)$(thing)猪灵$()→$(thing)猪灵蛮兵$()$(br)$(thing)村民$()→30%$(thing)掠夺者$()、60%$(thing)卫道士$()、10%$(thing)唤魔者$()$(br)$(thing)悦灵$()→$(thing)恼鬼$()$(br)$(thing)蝙蝠$()→$(thing)幻翼$()$(br)$(thing)马$()→10%$(thing)僵尸马$()、90%$(thing)骷髅马$()$(br)$(thing)蠹虫$()→$(thing)末影螨$()$(br)$(thing)骷髅$()→→20%$(thing)凋零骷髅$()、80%$(thing)流浪者$()",
    {
      "type": "patchouli:multiblock",
      "anchor": "time_warp",
      "name": "时移",
      "multiblock": {
        "mapping": {
          "G": "anvilcraft:cursed_gold_block",
          "0": "anvilcraft:cursed_gold_block",
          "C": "minecraft:cauldron",
          "B": "anvilcraft:corrupted_beacon[lit=true]",
